User Stories for existing features:
As a seller, I want to put up a property listing and update the price if it isn't selling, so that I can attract more buyers and maximise my chances of making a sale.

As a buyer, I want to see the full price history and dates for a listing, so that I can assess whether a property is fairly priced and how long it has been on the market.

As a buyer, I want to search for properties by postcode, so that I can find homes in my preferred area.

As a buyer, I want to register as a purchaser on the platform, so that I can save my preferences and interact with property listings.


User Stories for future features:
As a buyer, I want to submit a formal offer on a listed property, so that the seller can review and accept or reject it.

As an agent, I want to see the zip codes that have the highest interest, so that I can identify where the most buyers are looking and target my property listings accordingly.

As a buyer, I want to see notifications when the listings price drops, so that I know when to purchase.
